[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"For better performance, previous chat history has been compacted. CANVA BULK CREATE LABEL SYSTEM - IMMEDIATE DEPLOYMENT CRITICAL FILE DELIVERED ✅ LUMIERE-SOUL-CANVA-BULK-CREATE-TEMPLATE.csv Location: Already saved to your outputs Purpose: Batch-create all 12 professional candle labels with perfect consistency Status: READY FOR IMMEDIATE USE COMPLETE CANVA BULK CREATE SOP PHASE 1: TEMPLATE SETUP IN CANVA (20 minutes - ONE TIME ONLY) Step\tAction\tClick-by-Click Instructions\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tVisual Reference 1\tAccess Canva\t1. Go to canva.com 2. Click \"Create a design\" 3. Click \"Custom size\" 4. Enter Width: 3 inches, Height: 4 inches 5. Click \"Create new design\"\tWidth: 3, Height: 4, Unit: inches\tBlank 3x4\" canvas opens\tCanva editor with rulers showing 3\"x4\" dimensions 2\tSet Background\t1. Click canvas background 2. Click color picker in top toolbar 3. Enter HEX: #F5F1E8 (cream) 4. Press Enter\tHEX code: F5F1E8\tCanvas background changes to cream\tUniform cream-colored canvas 3\tAdd Brand Name Element\t1. Press \"T\" key or click \"Text\" in left sidebar 2. Click \"Add a heading\" 3. Type: {Brand_Name} 4. Select text, change font to Playfair Display Bold 5. Size: 18pt 6. Color: #2C2C2C (charcoal) 7. Drag to top center of canvas 8. Click \"···\" menu → Rename → Name it exactly: Brand_Name\tText content: {Brand_Name} Font: Playfair Display Bold Size: 18pt Color: #2C2C2C\tText box named \"Brand_Name\" at top center\tText element showing \"{Brand_Name}\" in charcoal at top 4\tAdd Product Name Element\t1. Press \"T\" key 2. Click \"Add a heading\" 3. Type: {Product_Name} 4. Select text, change font to Cormorant Garamond Bold 5. Size: 36pt 6. Color: #2C2C2C 7. Drag to center of canvas (vertically centered, horizontally centered) 8. Rename element to: Product_Name\tText content: {Product_Name} Font: Cormorant Garamond Bold Size: 36pt Color: #2C2C2C\tText box named \"Product_Name\" at center\tLarge elegant product name centered 5\tAdd Tagline Element\t1. Press \"T\" key 2. Click \"Add a subheading\" 3. Type: {Tagline} 4. Font: Montserrat Light Italic 5. Size: 10pt 6. Color: #D4AF37 (gold) 7. Position: Below product name, centered 8. Rename to: Tagline\tText: {Tagline} Font: Montserrat Light Italic Size: 10pt Color: #D4AF37\tGold tagline below product name\tItalic gold text \"Illuminate Your Story\" 6\tAdd Scent Notes Section\t1. Press \"T\" key 2. Click \"Add body text\" 3. Type: {Scent_Note_1} 4. Font: Montserrat Regular 5. Size: 10pt 6. Color: #2C2C2C 7. Position: Bottom left (0.25\" from left edge, 1\" from bottom) 8. Rename to: Scent_Note_1 9. Duplicate this element (Ctrl+D or Cmd+D) twice 10. Rename copies to Scent_Note_2 and Scent_Note_3 11. Stack vertically with 0.15\" spacing 12. Edit text to {Scent_Note_2} and {Scent_Note_3}\t3 text elements Font: Montserrat Regular Size: 10pt Spacing: 0.15\" between\t3 stacked scent note placeholders at bottom left\tVertical list of scent notes in charcoal 7\tAdd Burn Time Element\t1. Press \"T\" key 2. Add body text: {Burn_Time} 3. Font: Montserrat Medium 4. Size: 12pt 5. Color: #2C2C2C 6. Position: Bottom right (0.25\" from right edge, 1.2\" from bottom) 7. Rename to: Burn_Time\tText: {Burn_Time} Font: Montserrat Medium Size: 12pt\tBurn time text at bottom right\t\"50-Hour Burn Time\" bottom right 8\tAdd Size Element\t1. Press \"T\" key 2. Add body text: {Size} 3. Font: Montserrat Regular 4. Size: 10pt 5. Color: #2C2C2C 6. Position: Below Burn_Time (aligned right, 0.15\" spacing) 7. Rename to: Size\tText: {Size} Font: Montserrat Regular Size: 10pt\tSize text below burn time\t\"9oz\" aligned right 9\tAdd Hand Poured Badge\t1. Press \"T\" key 2. Add body text: {Hand_Poured} 3. Font: Montserrat SemiBold 4. Size: 8pt 5. Color: #D4AF37 (gold) 6. Position: Below Size (aligned right, 0.15\" spacing) 7. Rename to: Hand_Poured\tText: {Hand_Poured} Font: Montserrat SemiBold Size: 8pt Color: #D4AF37\tGold \"hand poured\" badge\tSmall gold badge \"HAND POURED\" 10\tAdd Decorative Border\t1. Click \"Elements\" in left sidebar 2. Search \"frame border elegant\" 3. Select simple gold frame/border 4. Resize to fit entire label (leave 0.1\" margin) 5. Change color to #D4AF37 (gold) 6. Send to back (Right-click → Layer → Send to back) 7. Rename to: Border\tElement: Frame/border Color: #D4AF37 Position: Full label with margins\tGold elegant border around label\tThin gold frame around all content 11\tAdd Illustration Element\t1. Click \"Elements\" 2. Search: {Illustration_Element} (will vary per product) 3. Select simple line-art style icon 4. Color: #D4AF37 (gold) 5. Size: 0.5\" x 0.5\" 6. Position: Between brand name and product name (centered) 7. Rename to: Illustration_Element\tElement type: Line art icon Size: 0.5\" x 0.5\" Color: #D4AF37\tSmall gold decorative icon\tGold candle flame or relevant icon 12\tVerify Element Names\t1. Click \"Layers\" panel (bottom right) 2. Verify these exact names exist: - Brand_Name - Product_Name - Tagline - Scent_Note_1 - Scent_Note_2 - Scent_Note_3 - Burn_Time - Size - Hand_Poured - Border - Illustration_Element\t11 named elements visible in Layers panel\tAll elements correctly named\tLayers panel shows all named elements 13\tSave as Template\t1. Click \"File\" → \"Save as template\" 2. Name: Lumiere Soul Label Master 3. Click \"Save\" 4. Note the template URL\tTemplate name: Lumiere Soul Label Master\tTemplate saved to your account\tTemplate appears in your Canva templates PHASE 2: BULK CREATE IMPORT (5 minutes) Step\tAction\tClick-by-Click Instructions\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tCritical Notes 1\tOpen Bulk Create\t1. Open your saved template \"Lumiere Soul Label Master\" 2. Click \"Apps\" in left sidebar 3. Search \"Bulk Create\" 4. Click \"Bulk Create\" app 5. Click \"Open\"\tN/A\tBulk Create panel opens on right side\tIf Bulk Create isn't available, you need Canva Pro (required for this feature) 2\tImport CSV\t1. In Bulk Create panel, click \"Upload CSV\" 2. Navigate to LUMIERE-SOUL-CANVA-BULK-CREATE-TEMPLATE.csv 3. Click \"Open\" 4. Wait for upload (5-10 seconds)\tFile: LUMIERE-SOUL-CANVA-BULK-CREATE-TEMPLATE.csv\tCSV data appears in Bulk Create panel\tFile must be CSV format (not Excel .xlsx) 3\tMap Columns to Elements\tCanva will auto-detect matching names. Verify mappings: 1. Brand_Name → Brand_Name ✓ 2. Product_Name → Product_Name ✓ 3. Tagline → Tagline ✓ 4. Scent_Note_1 → Scent_Note_1 ✓ 5. Scent_Note_2 → Scent_Note_2 ✓ 6. Scent_Note_3 → Scent_Note_3 ✓ 7. Burn_Time → Burn_Time ✓ 8. Size → Size ✓ 9. Hand_Poured → Hand_Poured ✓ If any aren't mapped, manually click dropdown and select correct element\tAll column headers match element names exactly\tAll 9 data columns mapped to template elements\tIf mappings fail, check element names in template exactly match CSV column headers 4\tPreview Results\t1. Click \"Preview\" button 2. Scroll through all 12 label previews 3. Check for: - Text not cut off - Consistent spacing - Proper font rendering - Gold accents visible\tN/A\tPreview shows all 12 unique labels with correct data\tIf text is cut off, go back to template and adjust text box sizes 5\tGenerate All Labels\t1. Click \"Generate\" button 2. Wait for processing (30-60 seconds for 12 labels) 3. Canva creates 12 separate pages in one document\tN/A\tMulti-page document with 12 unique labels\tEach page represents one finished label ready for download PHASE 3: DOWNLOAD & DEPLOY (10 minutes) Step\tAction\tClick-by-Click Instructions\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tDelivery Method 1\tDownload Labels\t1. Click \"Share\" button (top right) 2. Click \"Download\" 3. File type: PNG 4. Quality: High 5. Check \"All pages\" 6. Click \"Download\" 7. File saves as ZIP containing 12 PNG files\tFormat: PNG Quality: High Pages: All (12)\tZIP file with 12 individual PNG files named \"Lumiere-Soul-Label-Master_Page-1.png\" through \"Page-12.png\"\tDownloads to your computer 2\tRename Files\t1. Extract ZIP file 2. Rename each PNG to match SKU: - Page-1 → LUM-CEL-001.png - Page-2 → LUM-CEL-002.png - Page-3 → LUM-CEL-003.png - Page-4 → LUM-MED-001.png - Page-5 → LUM-MED-002.png - Page-6 → LUM-MED-003.png - Page-7 → LUM-FUN-001.png - Page-8 → LUM-FUN-002.png - Page-9 → LUM-FUN-003.png - Page-10 → LUM-MEN-001.png - Page-11 → LUM-MEN-002.png - Page-12 → LUM-MEN-003.png\t12 PNG files with page numbers\t12 PNG files with SKU-based filenames\tOrganized by SKU for easy PrintedMint upload 3\tUpload to PrintedMint\t1. Log into PrintedMint account 2. Go to \"My Products\" or \"Product Dashboard\" 3. Click \"9oz Amber Glass Candle\" 4. Click \"Upload Label Artwork\" 5. Drag and drop LUM-CEL-001.png first 6. Verify preview shows correct label 7. Repeat for all 12 SKUs\t12 PNG files (3\" x 4\" at 300 DPI)\tEach product has label artwork uploaded and ready\tPrintedMint validates dimensions automatically 4\tVerify PrintedMint Specs\tFor each uploaded label: 1. Check \"Artwork Status\" shows ✓ green checkmark 2. Verify dimensions: 3\" x 4\" 3. Verify resolution: 300 DPI minimum 4. Click \"Save\" for each product\tN/A\tAll 12 products show \"Ready for Production\" status\tIf any show warnings, re-export from Canva at higher quality 5\tTest Order\t1. In PrintedMint, click \"Order Sample\" 2. Select 1-2 products to test (recommended: one from each collection) 3. Complete checkout 4. Wait 5-8 days for delivery 5. Inspect label quality, adhesion, color accuracy\tSample quantity: 2 units Cost: ~$25-30 total\tPhysical samples arrive for quality check\tCRITICAL: Don't launch to customers until samples approved DESIGN SPECIFICATIONS SUMMARY Typography System Element\tFont Family\tWeight\tSize\tColor\tPurpose Brand Name\tPlayfair Display\tBold\t18pt\t#2C2C2C (Charcoal)\tConsistent brand identity across all labels Product Name\tCormorant Garamond\tBold\t36pt\t#2C2C2C (Charcoal)\tPrimary visual hierarchy - largest element Tagline\tMontserrat\tLight Italic\t10pt\t#D4AF37 (Gold)\tBrand message with elegant accent color Scen