n time\tBetter fit for smaller label ✅ 50-hour burn time\t✅ 50-hour burn time\tVERIFIED CORRECT per PrintedMint specs UPDATED CANVA SETUP (CRITICAL CHANGES) PHASE 1: Template Setup - CORRECTED DIMENSIONS Step\tAction\tCORRECTED Instructions\tExpected Input\tCritical Notes 1\tCreate Canvas\t1. Go to canva.com 2. Click \"Create a design\" 3. Click \"Custom size\" 4. Enter Width: 2.75 inches, Height: 2.25 inches 5. Click \"Create new design\"\tWidth: 2.75, Height: 2.25, Unit: inches\tThis is the OFFICIAL PrintedMint label size 2\tBrand Name\tFont: Playfair Display Bold Size: 14pt (not 18pt) Color: #2C2C2C Position: 0.15\" from top, centered\tReduced from 18pt to 14pt\tSmaller canvas = smaller fonts 3\tProduct Name\tFont: Cormorant Garamond Bold Size: 24pt (not 36pt) Color: #2C2C2C Position: Vertically centered (1.125\" from top)\tReduced from 36pt to 24pt\tThis is your main visual element 4\tTagline\tFont: Montserrat Light Italic Size: 8pt (not 10pt) Color: #D4AF37\tReduced from 10pt to 8pt\tGold accent below product name 5\tScent Notes\tFont: Montserrat Regular Size: 8pt (not 10pt) Position: 0.2\" from left edge, 0.4\" from bottom\t3 stacked elements, 0.1\" spacing\tScaled down for smaller label 6\tBurn Time\tFont: Montserrat Medium Size: 10pt (not 12pt) Position: 0.2\" from right edge, 0.5\" from bottom\tReduced from 12pt to 10pt\tKey benefit remains prominent 7\tSize (\"9oz\")\tFont: Montserrat Regular Size: 8pt Position: Below burn time, 0.1\" spacing\tSize specification\tAligned right with burn time 8\tHand Poured Badge\tFont: Montserrat SemiBold Size: 7pt (not 8pt) Color: #D4AF37 Position: Below size, 0.1\" spacing\tReduced from 8pt to 7pt\tSmall gold quality badge 9\tIllustration Icon\tSize: 0.4\" x 0.4\" (not 0.5\" x 0.5\") Color: #D4AF37 Position: Between brand and product name, centered\tReduced from 0.5\" to 0.4\"\tScaled for smaller label 10\tBorder\tGold frame (#D4AF37) Margin: 0.08\" all sides (not 0.1\")\tTighter margins for smaller canvas\tThin elegant frame VISUAL LAYOUT GUIDE (2.75\" x 2.25\" Label) Copy ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ 0\" Top │                 LUMIÈRE SOUL (14pt)                   │ 0.15\" │                      [icon]                           │ 0.5\" │              Midnight Rose (24pt)                     │ 1.125\" (CENTER) │         Illuminate Your Story (8pt gold)              │ 1.5\" │                                                        │ │ Rose Petals            50-Hour Burn Time (10pt)      │ 1.75\" │ Vanilla Cream                    9oz (8pt)           │ 1.9\" │ Amber Musk              HAND POURED (7pt gold)       │ 2.05\" └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ 2.25\" Bottom 0\"                                                  2.75\" WHAT TO DO NOW Delete the old 3\" x 4\" Canva template (wrong dimensions) Follow Phase 1 SOP above with CORRECTED dimensions (2.75\" x 2.25\") Use the new corrected CSV file I just created Everything else stays the same (Bulk Create process, download, upload to PrintedMint) BURN TIME SUMMARY (For Your Reference) Question\tAnswer\tSource Does 9oz burn for 50 hours?\t✅ YES - 50 hours\tPrintedMint Official Specs Does 4oz burn for 20 hours?\t✅ YES - 20 hours\tPrintedMint Official Specs Are you using 4oz candles?\t❌ NO - All 12 SKUs are 9oz\tYour product lineup Is \"50-Hour Burn Time\" correct for your labels?\t✅ YES - 100% accurate\tAll products use 9oz = 50 hours CRITICAL: IF YOU EXPAND TO 4OZ CANDLES IN FUTURE 4oz Amber Jar Specifications (for reference): Burn Time: 20 hours Label Size: 1.75\" x 2\" (DIFFERENT from 9oz) Cost: $6.50/unit (vs $11.25 for 9oz) Use case: Travel size, gift sets, sample collections You would need a SEPARATE Canva template for 4oz labels due to different dimensions. Your quality control instinct was spot-on - always verify manufacturer specs before going to production. This is exactly the kind of attention to detail that builds customer trust and avoids costly mistakes. 🎯 put this all int